<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; color: #334155;">
  <h2 style="color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 12px;">Admin Login Verification</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">You are attempting to log in to the SINOWER Admin Dashboard. Please use the following verification code:</p>
  
  <div style="background-color: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #2563eb;"><%= @otp %></span>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">This code will expire in 5 minutes. If you did not request this login, please change your password immediately.</p>
  
  <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 32px 0;">
  
  <h2 style="color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 12px;">后台登录验证</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">您正在尝试登录 SINOWER 后台管理系统。请使用以下验证码：</p>
  
  <div style="background-color: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #2563eb;"><%= @otp %></span>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">此验证码将在 5 分钟后失效。如果这不是您本人的操作，请立即更改您的密码。</p>
</div>